* Binder to receive a list that has a large number of {@link Parcelable} items.
 *
 * It's similar to {@link android.content.pm.ParceledListSlice}, but transactions are performed in
 * the opposite direction.
 *
 * @param <T> the type of {@link Parcelable}
 * @hide

methods.name: protected boolean onTransact(int code, Parcel data, Parcel reply, int flags) throws RemoteException
public static void send(@NonNull IBinder binder, @NonNull List<T> list) throws RemoteException
